element elementor-element-5a8138cc envato-kit-80-space-triangle elementor-hidden-phone elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"5a8138cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-29ba988a\" data-id=\"29ba988a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b8876f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4b8876f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Choose Tax Expert Advisor for TDS and PF\/ESI Services?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8ffa6b elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"b8ffa6b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d7b6702 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1d7b6702\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong><em>Expertise<\/em><\/strong>: Our team of tax professionals and compliance experts specializes in TDS, PF, and ESI compliance. We possess a deep understanding of the applicable laws and regulations to provide accurate and up-to-date advice.<\/p><p><strong><em>Comprehensive Solutions<\/em><\/strong>: We offer end-to-end solutions for TDS, PF, and ESI compliance, covering a wide range of services from registration and calculation to filing and audit support. Our services are suitable for businesses of all sizes and industries.<\/p><p><strong><em>Customized Approach<\/em><\/strong>: We recognize that every business has unique payroll and compliance needs. Our approach is highly personalized, ensuring that we tailor our services to your specific requirements and industry standards.<\/p><p><strong><em>Accuracy and Timeliness<\/em><\/strong>: Accuracy in TDS calculations and timely compliance with PF and ESI regulations are crucial to avoid penalties and fines. We prioritize precision and adherence to deadlines in our services.<\/p><p><strong>Our Range of TDS, PF, and ESI Services:<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>TDS (Tax Deducted at Source) Services:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li><p><strong>TDS Calculation and Deduction<\/strong>: We calculate TDS accurately for salaries, rent, interest, and other payments as per income tax laws. We ensure that TDS is deducted at the correct rates and deposited with the government.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>TDS Return Filing<\/strong>: We assist in filing TDS returns, including Form 24Q, 26Q, and 27Q, as required for salaries, non-salary payments, and foreign payments. We ensure that your TDS returns are filed accurately and on time.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>TDS Compliance Review<\/strong>: We conduct regular reviews to ensure that your TDS compliance aligns with the latest regulations and amendments. Our goal is to minimize errors and risks associated with TDS compliance.<\/p><\/li><\/ol><p><strong>PF (Provident Fund) and ESI (Employee State Insurance) Services:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li><p><strong>PF Registration and Compliance<\/strong>: We guide you through the PF registration process and help you maintain compliance with the Employees&#8217; Provident Fund Organization (EPFO). We assist in the calculation and deposit of monthly contributions.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>ESI Registration and Compliance<\/strong>: We facilitate ESI registration for employers and provide ongoing compliance support. We ensure timely filing of ESI contributions and help manage employee claims.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Audit Support<\/strong>: If your business is subject to PF or ESI audits, our experts can assist you during the audit process, helping you prepare documentation and respond to audit queries.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>PF and ESI Advisory<\/strong>: We provide expert advice on PF and ESI matters, including eligibility, contribution rates, and compliance requirements. Our goal is to help you make informed decisions and avoid non-compliance.<\/p><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-26495d elementor-position-left elementor-vertical-align-middle elementor-view-default elementor-mobile-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"26495d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https:\/\/taxexpertadvisors.com\/wp-content\/plugins\/elementor\/assets\/css\/widget-icon-box.min.css\">\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t<span  class=\"elementor-icon elementor-animation-\">\n\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-check\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\tOur Commitment to Your Compliance and Efficiency\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-el